00:14:11,333 --> 00:14:14,375
Seriously, Yaya; you have no
concept of how people work!

243
00:14:15,500 --> 00:14:17,708
[YAYA] But-- but that vixen!

244
00:14:17,791 --> 00:14:19,125
At any rate,

245
00:14:19,208 --> 00:14:21,166
tomorrow I plan to start
really looking into this case.

246
00:14:21,250 --> 00:14:24,666
Given everything I've seen and
heard about Cannibal Candy, I--

247
00:14:24,750 --> 00:14:27,666
No, we have
to find this killer.

248
00:14:27,750 --> 00:14:29,458
Are you with me?

249
00:14:29,541 --> 00:14:31,208
Yes!

250
00:14:39,250 --> 00:14:40,666
[RAISHIN] Charlotte?

251
00:14:41,666 --> 00:14:44,208
What're you doing
over here so late?

252
00:14:45,250 --> 00:14:46,458
Guh--!

253
00:14:46,541 --> 00:14:47,166
[RAISHIN] Yes?

254
00:14:47,250 --> 00:14:48,833
Go out with me!

255
00:14:50,208 --> 00:14:52,541
[CHARLOTTE] Rather,
I'll allow you to take me out.

256
00:14:52,625 --> 00:14:54,833
Tomorrow perhaps.
After lessons are finished.

257
00:14:54,916 --> 00:14:55,625
Huh?

258
00:14:55,708 --> 00:14:57,916
[YAYA]
Wha--? Nuh-- No!

259
00:14:58,000 --> 00:15:00,583
Thank you for the lovely offer,
but no, no, no, no!

260
00:15:00,666 --> 00:15:01,458
[RAISHIN] Yeah sure.

261
00:15:01,541 --> 00:15:04,000
Sounds good. I'll see you then.

262
00:15:04,791 --> 00:15:07,791
Excellent, I shall
hold you to it.

263
00:15:11,625 --> 00:15:12,958
[YAYA] How could you?

264
00:15:13,041 --> 00:15:16,916
You're so cruel to Yaya
after all she's done for you!

265
00:15:20,458 --> 00:15:22,625
Interesting spot
to choose for a date.

266
00:15:22,708 --> 00:15:23,791
Hmph!

267
00:15:23,875 --> 00:15:24,916
Poor, blind fool.

268
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:27,666
This isn't a date. It's a trap.

269
00:15:27,750 --> 00:15:29,750
[RAISHIN] Actually,
I had assumed as much.

270
00:15:29,833 --> 00:15:30,833
Don't be alarmed.

271
00:15:30,916 --> 00:15:32,583
You're perfectly safe,
I assure you.

272
00:15:32,666 --> 00:15:34,500
Should the villain appear,
I'll handle it.

273
00:15:34,583 --> 00:15:37,500
You just stand there
looking helpless.

274
00:15:37,583 --> 00:15:38,500
Now I see.

275
00:15:38,583 --> 00:15:39,875
You don't have any
friends, do you?

276
00:15:39,958 --> 00:15:41,750
[CHARLOTTE]
Why would you say that?

277
00:15:42,250 --> 00:15:43,750
[RAISHIN] You needed help
with this plan of yours,

278
00:15:43,833 --> 00:15:44,958
and you came to me.

279
00:15:45,041 --> 00:15:46,375
The guy you just met.

280
00:15:46,458 --> 00:15:49,333
I-- No! Y-You've
misread the situation!

281
00:15:49,416 --> 00:15:52,875
I'm helping you!
Ungrateful lout that you are.

282
00:15:52,958 --> 00:15:54,583
Okay, I get it.

283
00:15:54,666 --> 00:15:56,458
You heard Felix offered
me a festival entry

284
00:15:56,541 --> 00:15:58,041
if I could solve this case.

285
00:15:58,125 --> 00:16:00,166
Which means you must've
been eavesdropping.

286
00:16:00,250 --> 00:16:03,416
[CHARLOTTE] Wha--
and if I was? What of it?

287
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,791
I think I'm done with this.

288
00:16:05,875 --> 00:16:07,208
Enough of playing detective.

289
00:16:07,291 --> 00:16:09,000
Let's go on that date instead.

290
00:16:09,791 --> 00:16:11,083
Wha-- What?

291
00:16:11,166 --> 00:16:13,750
How unbelievably forward of you!

292
00:16:13,833 --> 00:16:15,750
[RAISHIN] You're the
one who asked me out.

293
00:16:15,833 --> 00:16:17,000
Or does the daughter

294
00:16:17,083 --> 00:16:19,125
of the great Belew family
not keep her word?

295
00:16:19,208 --> 00:16:20,583
How dare you, sir!

296
00:16:20,666 --> 00:16:23,125
Fine then; name the place,
and I shall take you there.

297
00:16:23,208 --> 00:16:26,416
No, sirree!
Absolutely not!

298
00:16:26,500 --> 00:16:27,708
Yaya will chaperone you!

299
00:16:27,791 --> 00:16:29,750
I know.
Let's go into town.

300
00:16:29,833 --> 00:16:31,875
Into town?
Then Sigmund can't come.

301
00:16:31,958 --> 00:16:32,958
Correct.

302
00:16:33,041 --> 00:16:34,125
It's considered normal practice

303
00:16:34,208 --> 00:16:37,208
to not bring one's
automaton on dates.

304
00:16:39,333 --> 00:16:42,666
Ah... I wouldn't be so
boorish as to ruin your fun.

305
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:44,416
Have a good time.

306
00:16:47,166 --> 00:16:48,916
What're you--?
That's my hand!

307
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,875
And this is a date.

308
00:16:51,333 --> 00:16:52,541
[CHARLOTTE]
Let me go this instant!

309
00:16:52,625 --> 00:16:54,166
[RAISHIN] Quit flailing.

310
00:16:57,125 --> 00:17:00,166
Y'might try having a bit
more faith in your master.

311
00:17:01,125 --> 00:17:02,416
Does he even deserve it?

312
00:17:02,500 --> 00:17:04,916
Trust me when I say
I am an accurate judge

313
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,750
of a person's character.

314
00:17:06,833 --> 00:17:10,333
I have had a hundred-fifty years
on this earth to figure it out.

315
00:17:10,416 --> 00:17:12,500
There was no lust in
his eyes when they left.

316
00:17:12,583 --> 00:17:14,166
None? Really?

317
00:17:14,250 --> 00:17:16,416
[SIGMUND] Really.
Though I must admit,

318
00:17:16,500 --> 00:17:19,375
boys his age are
unpredictable at best.

319
00:17:19,458 --> 00:17:21,041
No denyin' that.

320
00:17:21,125 --> 00:17:22,541
So I suppose
it's always possible

321
00:17:22,625 --> 00:17:24,625
something may
happen between 'em.

322
00:17:25,375 --> 00:17:26,500
[YAYA] Yaya knew it!

323
00:17:26,583 --> 00:17:28,583
[SIGMUND] We are not
human, you and I.

324
00:17:28,666 --> 00:17:30,750
You may be more or less
human both in appearance

325
00:17:30,833 --> 00:17:33,250
and functionality,
but you mustn't forget

326
00:17:33,333 --> 00:17:36,041
that you will never
actually be one of them.

327
00:17:36,125 --> 00:17:38,416
Yaya knows
that already too!

328
00:17:39,250 --> 00:17:41,416
Automatons operate
on magical power supplied

329
00:17:41,500 --> 00:17:43,208
to us by our puppeteers.

330
00:17:43,291 --> 00:17:46,541
Given that, it's natural to feel
great affection for your master,

331
00:17:46,625 --> 00:17:49,916
but I do not understand how
you came to be so obsessed.

332
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:52,625
Yaya cares for
Raishin, that's all.

333
00:17:52,708 --> 00:17:54,708
Yaya won't say more out loud.

334
00:17:55,791 --> 00:17:58,166
[SIGMUND] At any rate, our
masters aren't here right now,

335
00:17:58,250 --> 00:18:00,416
and Cannibal Candy
is still on the loose.

336
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:02,375
We must be careful.

337
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:12,666
[CHARLOTTE] I don't know
about you, but I'm famished.

338
00:18:12,750 --> 00:18:13,833
Let's go back.

339
00:18:14,583 --> 00:18:16,125
Why? We can eat here.

340
00:18:16,208 --> 00:18:17,416
Come on, I'll even treat.

341
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:20,041
[CHARLOTTE] I don't take
charity from lechers!

342
00:18:20,125 --> 00:18:22,708
[stomach growls]

343
00:18:22,791 --> 00:18:24,666
[CHARLOTTE] Oh, fine, let's eat!
But I'll have you know,

344
00:18:24,750 --> 00:18:27,500
I will never forgive you
for this embarrassment!

345
00:18:32,541 --> 00:18:34,500
[CHARLOTTE]
It looks divine.

346
00:18:38,291 --> 00:18:41,375
Out of curiosity,
the other day,

347
00:18:41,458 --> 00:18:43,291
why did you eat
lunch at my table?

348
00:18:43,375 --> 00:18:45,208
Just seemed like the
natural progression.

349
00:18:45,291 --> 00:18:47,583
Of what?
We were hardly friends.

350
00:18:47,666 --> 00:18:48,875
First, I yelled at you,

351
00:18:48,958 --> 00:18:50,458
then you challenged
me to a duel,

352
00:18:50,541 --> 00:18:52,666
then you insist
we dine together?

353
00:18:52,750 --> 00:18:55,000
That could only make
sense to a blithering idiot.

354
00:18:55,083 --> 00:18:57,791
I believe I'll take
that as a compliment.

355
00:18:58,833 --> 00:19:01,250
[CHARLOTTE] But why so
intent on my entry, anyway?

356
00:19:01,333 --> 00:19:03,875
There are a hundred of us
who qualified to compete.

357
00:19:03,958 --> 00:19:06,416
You could easily have picked
a lower-ranked target.

358
00:19:06,500 --> 00:19:10,083
[RAISHIN] Victory against
easy prey wouldn't mean as much.

359
00:19:10,166 --> 00:19:11,458
I tried to take
an entry by force,

360
00:19:11,541 --> 00:19:14,333
but at the expense
of another person.

361
00:19:14,416 --> 00:19:17,708
That'd be inexcusable without
also taking a personal risk.

362
00:19:17,791 --> 00:19:22,416
And even then it's
still inexcusable. Sorry.

363
00:19:22,500 --> 00:19:26,250
Yeah. I'm not explaining
myself very well.

364
00:19:26,333 --> 00:19:27,583
When we first met,

365
00:19:27,666 --> 00:19:31,125
my impression was you were
a tough person to read.

366
00:19:31,208 --> 00:19:33,958
But I've come to
realize you're just daft.

367
00:19:34,041 --> 00:19:36,708
So, any more
questions for me?

368
00:19:37,833 --> 00:19:39,666
Only one for now, I think.

369
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:41,208
About your fighting style.

370
00:19:41,291 --> 00:19:42,666
What is it called?

371
00:19:42,750 --> 00:19:45,208
I noticed you were fighting
alongside your puppet.

372
00:19:45,291 --> 00:19:47,250
Technically, that
was me cheating.

373
00:19:47,333 --> 00:19:49,125
I was creating a formation.

374
00:19:49,208 --> 00:19:53,083
It's my family's fighting
specialty, using group tactics.

375
00:19:53,166 --> 00:19:54,250
That's us.

376
00:19:54,333 --> 00:19:56,750
Pulling the strings
of a team of dolls.

377
00:20:00,250 --> 00:20:02,833
However, my training
was kind of rushed.

378
00:20:02,916 --> 00:20:04,833
I got my hands full
with just Yaya.

379
00:20:04,916 --> 00:20:07,041
The other day, I was
just using my own body

380
00:20:07,125 --> 00:20:09,000
in place of another doll.

381
00:20:09,083 --> 00:20:10,125
So it's a good thing I know

382
00:20:10,208 --> 00:20:12,000
a little something
about martial arts.

383
00:20:12,083 --> 00:20:14,083
What do you mean,
your training was "rushed"?

384
00:20:14,166 --> 00:20:15,875
[RAISHIN] Well,
I didn't start really studying

385
00:20:15,958 --> 00:20:17,916
until just over two years ago.

386
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:19,666
[CHARLOTTE] Huh? What?

387
00:20:19,750 --> 00:20:22,708
And you already want
to compete for Wise Man?

388
00:20:22,791 --> 00:20:25,541
I have my reasons.
Let's leave it at that.

389
00:20:26,125 --> 00:20:28,625
[RAISHIN] My turn.
Do you have a crush on Felix?

390
00:20:28,708 --> 00:20:30,375
[CHARLOTTE] Wha--? You--!

391
00:20:30,458 --> 00:20:32,708
Don't make me sound so common!

392
00:20:32,791 --> 00:20:36,000
My relationship with Felix
is nothing so vulgar as that!

393
00:20:36,083 --> 00:20:38,333
[RAISHIN] I don't see
anything vulgar about it.

394
00:20:38,416 --> 00:20:39,375
It's no big deal.

395
00:20:39,458 --> 00:20:41,208
That sort of thing
is human nature.

396
00:20:41,291 --> 00:20:43,416
[CHARLOTTE] I'm telling
you to drop it right now.

397
00:20:43,500 --> 00:20:47,375
Or I shall be forced to
cause you grievous bodily harm.

398
00:20:49,083 --> 00:20:53,208
Only sometimes, I make enemies
without realizing or meaning to.

399
00:20:53,291 --> 00:20:56,750
So, as head of the disciplinary
board, Felix worries about me.

400
00:20:56,833 --> 00:20:58,375
That's all.

401
00:21:00,083 --> 00:21:02,125
[RAISHIN] He's asked you
to go out with him, hasn't he?

402
00:21:02,208 --> 00:21:03,625
Why not accept?

403
00:21:03,708 --> 00:21:05,000
I can't do that!

404
00:21:05,083 --> 00:21:07,416
Don't you know how
popular Felix is?

405
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:08,666
With girls, I mean.

406
00:21:08,750 --> 00:21:10,708
The chits are practically
rabid about him.

407
00:21:10,791 --> 00:21:13,208
[RAISHIN] So you'd wind up
with even more enemies.

408
00:21:13,291 --> 00:21:14,291
Is that it?

409
00:21:14,375 --> 00:21:15,625
[CHARLOTTE] Precisely.

410
00:21:19,083 --> 00:21:20,041
[RAISHIN] What about you?

411
00:21:20,125 --> 00:21:21,666
Why do you want
to be the Wise Man?

412
00:21:23,916 --> 00:21:25,083
[CHARLOTTE] I have a dream.

413
00:21:25,166 --> 00:21:26,750
Something important.

414
00:21:26,833 --> 00:21:29,416
Something I'm willing to
get blood on my hands for.

415
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:31,291
[RAISHIN] Fair enough.

416
00:21:32,583 --> 00:21:34,250
[RAISHIN] Thank you for
coming shopping with me.

417
00:21:34,333 --> 00:21:35,708
You were a big help.

418
00:21:36,375 --> 00:21:37,666
[CHARLOTTE]
To be honest,

419
00:21:37,750 --> 00:21:40,166
I'm surprised buying her
a gift even occurred to you.

420
00:21:41,083 --> 00:21:42,041
What is it?

421
00:21:42,125 --> 00:21:43,291
Is she so terrifying you have

422
00:21:43,375 --> 00:21:45,708
to buy her presents
to placate her?

423
00:21:45,791 --> 00:21:47,333
Oh, I wouldn't say that.

424
00:21:47,416 --> 00:21:48,541
Not where she can hear me.

425
00:21:48,625 --> 00:21:50,666
You're pitiful.
You know that?

426
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:52,916
Ordered around by
your own automaton.

427
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:54,625
That's plain backwards.

428
00:21:56,500 --> 00:21:58,916
[CHARLOTTE] Look, about
what you said before,

429
00:21:59,000 --> 00:22:01,500
the reason you chose
to challenge my entry.

430
00:22:01,583 --> 00:22:02,666
[RAISHIN] Yeah?

431
00:22:02,750 --> 00:22:05,083
[CHARLOTTE] I want you
to know, I get it.

432
00:22:05,166 --> 00:22:06,166
You're still daft,

433
00:22:06,250 --> 00:22:09,416
but I understand
wanting to be punished.

434
00:22:10,666 --> 00:22:13,958
There are things in my past
I'm not proud of, either.

435
00:22:14,041 --> 00:22:15,166
Huh?

436
00:22:18,791 --> 00:22:19,625
No.

437
00:22:19,708 --> 00:22:21,708
Cannibal Candy!

438
00:22:22,208 --> 00:22:24,541
[RAISHIN] Didn't think
he'd strike again so soon!

439
00:22:26,958 --> 00:22:27,875
[RAISHIN] Yaya!

440
00:22:27,958 --> 00:22:29,083
[CHARLOTTE] Raishin!

